text: What's New, Scooby-Doo? is an American kids' TV show on Cartoon Network and Boomerang. The show's about humans: Fred, Daphne, Velma, and Shaggy, and their dog named Scooby-Doo, who like solving mysteries together. ==Cast== *Frank Welker - Scooby-Doo and Fred *Casey Kasem - Shaggy *Grey DeLisle-Griffin - Daphne *Mindy Cohn - Velma ==Episodes== Category:Scooby-Doo television series Category:2002 American television series debuts Category:2006 American television series endings Category:Kids WB series Category:Cartoon Network series
title: What's New, Scooby-Doo?
